    <p><span>Life Crossing: Fantasy Horizons, Rival Fantasy: Ever Crisis Academy Seven, and more.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Welcome to the 2025 edition of <a title="Companies > Gematsu" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/gematsu">Gematsu</a>‘s annual April Fools’ Day games industry jokes and gags roundup, featuring <em>Life Crossing: Fantasy Horizons</em> from <a title="Companies > LEVEL-5 [761 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/level-5">LEVEL-5</a>, <em>Rival Fantasy: Ever Crisis Academy Seven</em> from <a title="Companies > Square Enix [5,338 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/square-enix">Square Enix</a>, and more. <span id="more-954202"></span></p><p><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2024/03/april-fools-day-2024-compilation">April Fools’ Day 2024</a> | <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2023/03/april-fools-day-2023-compilation">2023</a> | <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2022/03/april-fools-day-2022-compilation" rel="noopener" target="_blank">2022</a> | <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2021/04/april-fools-day-2021-compilation">2021</a> | <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2020/04/april-fools-day-2020-compilation">2020</a> | <a href="https://gematsu.com/2019/03/april-fools-day-2019-compilation">2019</a> | <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/tag/april-fools-day" rel="noopener" target="_blank">More</a></p><p>(This post will be updated with new jokes throughout the day.)</p><p><strong>■ Added at Press Time</strong></p><p><strong>● <a title="Companies > Aiming [30 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/aiming">Aiming</a></strong></p><p><strong><em>The Eminence in Shadow: <a title="Companies > Mas" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/mas">Mas</a>ter of Garden</em></strong></p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p>Sanrio characters collaboration announced.</p><p><iframe title="【カゲマス】「ハローカゲマス！素敵なみんなに頼りたくて」PV" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/nNw-rgtICVQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>● <a title="Companies > Aniplex [273 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sony-group-corporation/sony-music-entertainment-japan/aniplex">Aniplex</a></strong></p><p><strong><em><a title="Series > Fate [66 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/series/fate">Fate</a>/Grand Order</em></strong></p><p>This year’s annual April Fools’ Day <em>Fate/Grand Order</em> spin-off game is the casual <a title="Genres > Action [2,614 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/action">action game</a> <em>Fate/Final Journey</em>. It is available now for iOS via <a href="https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/fate-final-journey/id6741059037" target="_blank">App Store</a> and Android via <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.aniplex.fatefinaljourney" target="_blank">Google Play</a>. It is a casual action game.</p><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/April-Fools-Day-2025_Fate-Final-Journey.jpg"></a></figure><p><strong><em><a title="Games > The Hundred Line: Last Defense Academy [7 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/the-hundred-line-last-defense-academy">The Hundred Line: Last Defense Academy</a></em></strong></p><p>Introducing <a title="Companies > Too Kyo Games [74 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/too-kyo-games">Too Kyo Games</a>‘ new employee and public relations character: Too Kyo-chan!</p><p><iframe title="Tookyo Games新入社員「トゥーキョーちゃん」紹介動画" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CBodDu0t5aE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong><em><a title="Games > Puella Magi Madoka Magica: Magia Exedra [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/puella-magi-madoka-magica-magia-exedra">Puella Magi Madoka Magica: Magia Exedra</a></em></strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Puella Magi Madoka Magica Magia Exedra | DANCE☆MAGICA Event PV" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/l-eKsdM6wWs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p>(Also available in <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bs4aDB2AWNM" target="_blank">Japanese</a>.)</p><p><strong>● <a title="Companies > Bandai Namco Entertainment [6,667 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/bandai-namco-entertainment">Bandai Namco Entertainment</a></strong></p><p><strong><em>Katamari</em> Series</strong></p><p>A collaboration between <em>That Time I Got Reincarnated as a Slime ISEKAI Memories</em> and the <em>Katamari</em> franchise has been announced.</p><p><strong>● <a title="Companies > BeXide [26 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/bexide">BeXide</a></strong></p><p><strong><em><a title="Games > The Fox's Way Home [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/the-foxs-way-home">The Fox’s Way Home</a></em></strong></p><p><em>The Fox’s Way Home</em> collaboration with <em>Wizardry Gaiden: The Five Ordeals</em> announced.</p><p><strong>● <a title="Companies > Cygames [274 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/cyberagent/cygames">Cygames</a></strong></p><p><strong><em><a title="Games > Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising [33 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/granblue-fantasy-versus-rising">Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising</a></em></strong></p><div><blockquote data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">FANBLUE GRANTASY RISES: VERSING RETURNS!</p><p>Back by popular demand, you can now obtain these illustrations for the entire roster from the in-game Rupie Shop!</p><p>(Please return to the title screen if they do not appear.)<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/GBVSR?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#GBVSR</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/ACBu?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#ACBu</a> <a href="https://t.co/EU5HcXFajP">pic.twitter.com/EU5HcXFajP</a></p><p>— GBVS/Granblue Fantasy Versus (@gbvs_official) <a href="https://twitter.com/gbvs_official/status/1906725925426704842?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 31, 2025</a></p></blockquote></div><p>(Also available in <a href="https://twitter.com/gbvs_official/status/1906725673139593583" target="_blank">Japanese</a>.)</p><p><strong>● <a title="Companies > Electronic Arts [1,765 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/electronic-arts">Electronic Arts</a></strong></p><p><strong><em>Apex Legends</em> (Japan)</strong></p><p>Valkyrie’s voice will be changed to Kansai dialect in the next update.</p><p>https://twitter.com/eajapan/status/1906723177042243777</p><p><strong>● <a title="Companies > Entergram [200 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/entergram">Entergram</a></strong></p><p><strong>Nekura na Classmate ga Ore no <a title="Games > Ib [7 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/ib">Ib</a>ukuro o Tsukande Hanashite Kurenai</strong></p><p>Announcing the new <a title="Genres > Visual Novel [545 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/visual-novel">visual novel</a> <em>Youkya-na Classmate ga Ore no Ibukuro o Tsukande Hanashite Kurenai</em>.</p><p><strong>● <a title="Companies > Kadokawa Corporation [598 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/kadokawa-corporation">Kadokawa Corporation</a></strong></p><p><strong><em>Re:Zero – Starting Life in Another World</em></strong></p><p>Announcing the <a title="Genres > Otome [109 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/visual-novel/otome">otome visual novel</a> <em>Re:Zero – School Life in Another World</em>. Coming soon…?</p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="乙女ゲーム『Re:ゼロから始める異世界学園生活』リリース決定!? | スペシャルPV公開" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fAemUoPuDJw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>● LEVEL-5</strong></p><p><strong><em><a title="Games > FANTASY LIFE i: The Girl Who Steals Time [13 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/fantasy-life-i-the-girl-who-steals-time">FANTASY LIFE i: The Girl Who Steals Time</a></em></strong></p><p>Introducing the Fantasy Getaway Package. <em>FANTASY LIFE i: The Girl Who Steals Time</em> is now <em>Life Crossing: Fantasy Horizons</em>.</p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Introducing the Fantasy Getaway Package" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/69HlFW9RpJs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p>(Also available in <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pW_WW0qSMlw" target="_blank">Japanese</a>, <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DAsd9uReupw" target="_blank">Traditional Chinese</a>, <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kePsJvY-u-s" target="_blank">Simplified Chinese</a>.)</p><p><strong>● <a title="Companies > LOCOBIT [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/locobit">LOCOBIT</a></strong></p><p><strong><em><a title="Games > BUTTO BIRD [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/butto-bird">BUTTO BIRD</a></em></strong></p><p>Announcing <em>BUTTO BIRD Cassette Edition</em> for <a title="Platforms > NES [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/nes">Nintendo Entertainment System</a> (Famicom).</p><p><strong>● <a title="Companies > NEXTON [10 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/nexton">NEXTON</a></strong></p><p><strong>Novamicus</strong></p><p>A completely new original title is in development featuring illustrations by Itaru Hinoue. (This may or may not be a joke.)</p><p><strong>● PONOS</strong></p><p>Introducing the <a href="https://battlecats.club/special/aprilfool/2025/" target="_blank">Neko Nyaturn</a>, a new game system due out on February 22, 2222.</p><p>https://twitter.com/PONOS_GAME/status/1906723174525382933</p><p><strong>● <a title="Companies > SEGA [2,653 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sega">SEGA</a></strong></p><p><strong><em><a title="Series > Sonic the Hedgehog [56 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/series/sonic-the-hedgehog">Sonic the Hedgehog</a></em> (Japan)</strong></p><p>The April issue of the Weekly Hedgehog is out now, with stories like “Knuckles Hires a Gang of Thieves to Guard the Emerald!?” and “Rising Costs Mean More Rings Are Required to Get a 1UP!?”</p><p>https://twitter.com/SonicOfficialJP/status/1906723163993772461</p><p><strong>● <a title="Companies > SHIFT UP [26 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/shift-up">SHIFT UP</a></strong></p><p><strong><em>GODDESS OF VICTORY: NIKKE</em></strong></p><p><em>GODDESS OF VICTORY: NIKKE</em>‘s blockbuster movie, “FINAL BATTLE,” will be released on April 1!</p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="《FINAL BATTLE》 Premiering Soon!" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zqpNvHKb_20?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>SHIFT UP</strong></p><p>The newly launched SHIFT UP YouTube channel has surpassed one million subscribers.</p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="1 Million Subscribers! Thank you!!" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/g2m8T3o4N4k?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>● Square Enix</strong></p><p><strong><em><a title="Series > Dragon Quest [97 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/series/dragon-quest">Dragon Quest</a> Walk</em></strong></p><p>Bunmeido Tokyo collaboration announced.</p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="ドラゴンクエストウォーク×文明堂東京『文明堂歩劇場』" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/EMFIMVpfnqE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong><em><a title="Games > Final Fantasy VII: Ever Crisis [10 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/final-fantasy-vii-ever-crisis">Final Fantasy VII: Ever Crisis</a></em></strong></p><p>Announcing <a href="https://en.ffviiec.com/ec-academy" target="_blank"><em>Rival Fantasy: Ever Crisis Academy Seven</em></a> (title tentative) with the opening of two new schools in the city of Midgard: Midgard Seventh High School and Shinra Private Academy.</p><p>(Also available in <a href="https://twitter.com/FFVII_EC_JP/status/1906723157937115357" target="_blank">Japanese</a>.)</p><p><strong><em>NieR</em></strong></p><p>An 8-bit version of <em><a title="Games > NieR: Automata [117 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/nier-automata">NieR: Automata</a></em> is finally here.</p><p>https://twitter.com/NieR_JPN/status/1906723499248431474</p><p><strong>● <a title="Companies > Visual Arts [12 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/visual-arts">VisualArts</a></strong></p><p><strong>Key</strong></p><p>Announcing the release of the new movie <a href="https://key.prpage.jp/kagibeya/" target="_blank"><em>Key: Escape from the White Locked Room</em></a>, a new <a title="Genres > Horror [586 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/horror">horror</a> movie from the studio behind games like <em><a title="Games > Kanon [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/kanon">Kanon</a></em> and <em>Clannad</em>.</p><p>https://twitter.com/key_official/status/1906723196533121533</p><p><strong>● <a title="Companies > Wargaming [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/wargaming">Wargaming.net</a></strong></p><p><strong><em>War Thunder</em></strong></p><p>The long awaited and highly requested addition of infantry to the battlefields of <em>War Thunder</em> is finally here!</p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="The Next Big Thing for War Thunder / Trailer" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vZA0GkLNDeQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>● <a title="Companies > Yostar [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/yostar">Yostar</a></strong></p><p><strong><em>Azur Lane</em></strong></p><p>Announcing the new anime <a href="https://2nd.azurlane-bisoku.jp/" target="_blank"><em>Azur Lane: Bisoku Tensei!</em></a></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【エイプリルフール】新作アニメ『アズールレーン びそくてんせいっ！』PV" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/lCknfftoy2k?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
